ENDPOINTS:

addFileToTransaction
  - https://addfiletotransaction-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, groupID, transactionID, fileName
  - Attaches a file to a specific transaction in a group

addPayment
  - https://addpayment-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, groupId, fromId, toId, amount
  - Records a payment between two users and sends a notification email

confirmTransaction
  - https://confirmtransaction-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, groupID, transactionID
  - Confirms a pending transaction within a group

createTransaction
  - https://createtransaction-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, “request” (JSON stringified object)
  - Creates a new financial transaction within a group, ensuring balances match

currencyRate 
  - https://currencyrate-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, currencyID
  - Updates the exchange rate of a specified currency

deleteTransaction
  - https://deletetransaction-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, groupID, transactionID
  - Deletes a specified transaction from a group

extractInformation
  - https://extractinformation-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, fileName
  - Extracts expense details from an uploaded receipt image using AI

getGroupBalance
  - https://getgroupbalance-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, groupID
  - Retrieves the balance details of a group

getLoginAttempts
  - https://getloginattempts-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: email
  - Retrieves the number of failed login attempts for a given email

groupChange
  - https://groupchange-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, groupID, groupName, groupCurrency (name and currency are optional parameters)
  - Updates the name or currency of an existing group

groupCreate
  - https://groupcreate-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, groupName
  - Creates a new user group with the given name

groupDelete
  - https://groupdelete-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, groupID
  - Deletes a specified group

groupJoin
  - https://groupjoin-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, groupCode
  - Allows a user to join a group using an invitation code

groupLeave
  - https://groupleave-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, groupID
  - Allows a user to leave a group if their balance is zero

increaseLoginAttempts
  - https://increaseloginattempts-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: email
  - Increments the failed login attempt count for a given email

resetLoginAttempts
  - https://resetloginattempts-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: email
  - Resets the failed login attempt count for a given email 


scheduledFunctionCrontab
  - */5 * * * *
  - (no parameters internally fetches groupIDs and sends reminders)
  - A scheduled function that runs every 5 minutes to send reminders to group mmbers with outstanding balances

sendInvitation: 
  - https://sendinvitation-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, email, groupID
  - Sends an email invitation to a user to join a specific group using the group's invitation code

sendNewPassword
  - https://sendnewpassword-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: email
  - Sends a new password via email and updates the user's credentials

sendReminders
  - https://sendreminders-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, groupID
  - Sends reminder emails to users with outstanding balances in a group

updateRates
  - https://updaterates-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken
  - Updates currency exchange rates using an external API

userDelete
  - https://userdelete-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken
  - Deletes a user if they have no outstanding balances in any group

userLogin
  - https://userlogin-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken
  - Handles user login and sets a preferred currency

userRegistration
  - https://userregistration-icvq5uaeva-uc.a.run.app
  - Parameters: idToken, firstName, lastName
  - Registers a new user with first and last name, assigning a default currency
